name: Worm Dance Quilt
description:
This artwork is the first in a series of 4 NFTs that I made using (with permission) the artwork of my friend @EaEAa10.  You can see the original artwork here https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/204459.  

Hope you love the series as I had a bunch of fun making these pieces!

This NFT is also a Drop and Burn.  Originally 150 editions are being dropped and the burn will take place in about 4 hours, so we shall se how many editions survive the burn!
